children of the corn iv : the gathering is a 1996 american horror film directed by greg spence and starring naomi watts and brent jennings . it is the fourth film in the children of the corn series . the plot follows a medical student returning to her hometown in nebraska , where she finds the children to be falling under a mysterious mass illness connected to the town 's past . the film expands upon the origins of " he who walks behind the rows " . the film marked the first time naomi watts received first billing .